room_title: Escape room "Egyptian Mysteries" by Escape Haus in San Marcos
room_description: Your mentor, a world-renowned Egyptologist, has made a history-changing discovery. Before he can announce his discovery, he is kidnapped. Apparently, some very powerful factions want to keep this discovery hidden and are on the way to destroy your mentor's study. You have one hour to piece together the clues left behind that will lead you to where this discovery is hidden.
